</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"810772f28ced6fb5c61e9a4f5f53bfdd8bd0c8a6","tid":1544841,"uid":140000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"唱<span style=\"color: red;\">香港國</span>國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0d88789c7bfb36f3c45318eda366c71fd20aca","tid":1544841,"uid":57748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:51:24.000Z","msg":"入想睇波👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻"},{"pid":"13424abbb1243e5a141a80e6e7ae5d7979701285","tid":1544841,"uid":17522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"我係香港人呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想有一日見到港隊係世界盃到唱呢首國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d50f955dd6582f7f80ad82cd6a4fb4dedf30fca","tid":1544841,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T18:15:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dc8ebc0b6b7ce8b8afad9c1c20d5f973156d209","tid":1544841,"uid":149215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T18:15:56.000Z","msg":"［核彈]906全民太子站獻花，極重要！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544949</a>"},{"pid":"35e710b92d1ebabc612e3601fdc958f885b76615","tid":1544841,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:01:05.000Z","msg":"伊朗肯嚟？"},{"pid":"f7d7f79a720d599f3ff82a49dcc1580e23ed2d89","tid":1544841,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0